J&J’s Scios Unit Charged in Misbranding of Heart Drug Natrecor

-- B y   K a r e n   G u l l o
-- 
2011-07-08T22:51:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/j-j-s-scios-unit-charged-with-misbranding-of-its-heart-drug-natrecor.html
Johnson & Johnson (JNJ) ’s Scios unit was
charged with misbranding the heart drug Natrecor, federal
prosecutors in  San Francisco  said in a court filing alleging the
medicine’s labeling lacked adequate directions for use.  To contact the reporter on this story:
